lemma Algebra.epi_of_comp_epi {X Y Z : α} (f : Hom X Y) (g : Hom Y Z)
    (hfg : Epi (f ≫ g)) : Epi g := by sorry
```

These lemmas establish how monomorphisms and epimorphisms behave with respect to composition. The proofs are left as `sorry`.

